1220191,211,837,65,98,1,226,25,"Na,‘‘ dvādasahi ākārehi parisato kammāni vipajjantī’’ ti etassa vibhaṅge tesamanāmaṭṭhattā, ayamattho yasmā tattha tattha sarūpena vuttapāḷivaseneva sakkā jānituṃ, tasmā nayamukhaṃ dassetvā saṃkhittoti ayamassa yuttigavesanāti vuttaṃ. "
1220192,211,838,2,20,1,152,16,"Tatridaṃ vicāretabbaṃ– anupajjhāyakaṃ upasampādentā te bhikkhū yathāvuttanayena abhūtaṃ vatthuṃ kittayiṃsu, udāhu musāvādabhayā tāneva padāni na sāvesunti. "
1220193,211,838,21,46,1,137,17,"Kiñcettha– yadi tāva upajjhāyābhāvato na sāvesuṃ,‘‘ puggalaṃ na parāmasatī’’ ti vuttavipattippasaṅgo hoti, atha sāvesuṃ, musāvādo nesaṃ bhavatīti? "
1220194,211,838,47,64,1,102,11,"Vuccate– sāvesuṃyeva yathāvuttavipattippasaṅgabhayā,‘‘ kammaṃ pana na kuppatī’’ ti aṭṭhakathāyaṃ vuttattā ca. "
1220195,211,838,65,73,1,58,6,"Na, musāvādassa asambhavato, musāvādenapi kammasambhavato ca. "
1220196,211,838,74,80,1,52,6,Na hi sakkā musāvādena kammavipattisampattiṃ kātunti. 
1220197,211,838,81,94,1,90,9,Tasmā‘‘ anupajjhāyakaṃ upasampādentī’’ ti vacanassa ca ubhayadosavinimutto attho pariyesitabbo. 
1220198,211,839,2,39,1,263,26,"Ayañcettha yutti– yathā pubbe pabbajjupasampadupajjhāyesu vijjamānesupi upajjhāyaggahaṇakkamena aggahitattā‘‘ tena kho pana samayena bhikkhū anupajjhāyakan’’ tiādi vuttaṃ, tathā idhāpi upajjhāyassa vijjamānasseva sato aggahitattā‘‘ anupajjhāyakaṃ upasampādentī’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1220199,211,839,40,55,1,97,11,Kammavācācariyena pana‘‘ gahito tena upajjhāyo’’ ti saññāya upajjhāyaṃ kittetvā kammavācaṃ sāvetabbaṃ. 
1220200,211,839,56,99,1,384,40,"Kenaci vā kāraṇena kāyasāmaggiṃ adentassa upajjhāyassa chandaṃ gahetvā kammavācaṃ sāveti, upajjhāyo vā upasampadāpekkhassa upajjhaṃ datvā pacchā upasampanne tasmiṃ tādise vatthusmiṃ samanuyuñjiyamāno vā asamanuyuñjiyamāno vā upajjhāyadānato pubbe eva sāmaṇero paṭijānāti, sikkhāpaccakkhātako vā antimavatthuajjhāpannako vā paṭijānāti, chandahārakādayo viya upajjhāyo vā aññasīmāgato hoti. "
1220201,211,839,100,116,1,120,12,Kammavācā ruhatīti vatvā‘‘ anujānāmi bhikkhave paccantimesu janapadesu vinayadharapañcamena gaṇena upasampadan’’ ti vuttattā. 
1220202,211,839,117,130,1,100,9,Keci‘‘ vinayadharapañcamena upajjhāyena sannihiteneva bhavitabban’’ ti vadantīti porāṇagaṇṭhipade vuttaṃ. 
1220203,211,839,131,139,1,65,8,So ca pāṭho appamāṇo majjhimesu janapadesu tassa vacanassābhāvato. 
1220204,211,839,140,146,1,55,6,Asannihitepi upajjhāye kammavācā ruhatīti āpajjatīti ce? 
1220205,211,839,147,148,1,2,1,Na. 
