1220207,211,839,151,162,1,63,7,Kammasampattiyaṃ‘‘ puggalaṃ parāmasatī’’ ti vuttapāṭhova no pamāṇaṃ. 
1220208,211,839,163,178,1,135,14,"Na hi tattha asannihito upajjhāyasaṅkhāto puggalo parāmasanaṃ arahati, tasmā tattha saṅghaparāmasanaṃ viya puggalaparāmasanaṃ veditabbaṃ. "
1220209,211,839,179,193,1,138,12,"Saṅghena gaṇena upajjhāyena upasampādenti tesaṃ atthato puggalattā, paṇḍakādiupajjhāyena upasampādenti upasampādanakāle aviditattāti porāṇā. "
1220210,211,840,2,30,1,186,17,"Apattacīvaraṃ {upasampādentī}ti kammavācācariyo‘‘ paripuṇṇassa pattacīvaran’’ ti saññāya, kevalaṃ atthasampattiṃ anapekkhitvā santapadanīhārena vā‘‘ paripuṇṇassa pattacīvaran’’ ti kammavācaṃ sāveti. "
