1220223,211,841,190,192,1,10,2,Kiṃ bahunā? 
1220224,211,842,2,34,1,187,19,"Ayaṃ panettha sāro– yathā pubbe pabbajjādhikāre vattamāne pabbajjābhilāpaṃ upacchinditvā‘‘ paṇḍako, bhikkhave, anupasampanno na upasampādetabbo’’ tiādinā( mahāva.109) nayena upasampadavaseneva abhilāpo kato. "
1220225,211,842,35,71,1,325,32,"Theyyasaṃvāsakapade asambhavato kiñcāpi so na kato, pabbajjāva tattha katā, sabbattha pana upasampadābhilāpena adhippetā tadanubhāvato upasampadāya, pabbajjāya vāritāya upasampadā vāritā hotīti katvā, tathā idha upasampadādhikāre vattamāne upasampadābhilāpaṃ upacchinditvā upasampadameva sandhāya pabbajjābhilāpo katoti veditabbo. "
1220226,211,842,72,97,1,210,23,"Kāmaṃ so na kattabbo, mūgapade asambhavato tassa vasena ādito paṭṭhāya upasampadābhilāpova kattabbo viya dissati, tathāpi tasseva mūgapadassa vasena ādito paṭṭhāya pabbajjābhilāpova kato micchāgahaṇanivāraṇatthaṃ. "
