1220264,211,847,41,61,1,136,18,"Tasmā aññampi yaṃ kiñci tassa nāmaṃ pasiddhaṃ, tasmiṃ vā khaṇe sukhaggahaṇatthaṃ nāmaṃ paññāpitaṃ, taṃ sabbaṃ gahetvāpi anussāvanā kātabbā. "
1220265,211,847,62,97,1,204,24,"Yathā upajjhāyassa, evaṃ upasampadāpekkhassāpi gottādināmena taṅkhaṇikanāmena ca anussāvanaṃ kātuṃ vaṭṭati, tasmimpi khaṇe‘‘ ayaṃ tisso’’ ti vā‘‘ nāgo’’ ti vā nāmaṃ karontehi anusāsakasammutito paṭhamameva kātabbaṃ. "
1220266,211,847,98,139,1,234,29,"Evaṃ akatvāpi antarāyikadhammānusāsanapucchanakālesu‘‘ kinnāmosi, ahaṃ bhante nāgo nāma, ko nāmo te upajjhāyo, upajjhāyo me bhante tisso nāmā’’ tiādinā viññāpentena ubhinnampi citte‘‘ mametaṃ nāman’’ ti yathā saññaṃ uppajjati, evaṃ viññāpetabbaṃ. "
1220267,211,847,140,159,1,97,14,"Sace pana tasmiṃ khaṇe pakatināmena vatvā pacchā‘‘ tisso nāmā’’ ti apubbanāmena anussāveti, na vaṭṭati. "
1220268,211,848,2,35,1,273,28,Tattha ca kiñcāpi upajjhāyasseva nāmaṃ aggahetvā yena kenaci nāmena‘‘ tissassa upasampadāpekkho’’ tiādināpi puggale parāmaṭṭhe kammaṃ sukatameva hoti anupajjhāyakādīnaṃ upasampadākammaṃ viya upajjhāyassa abhāvepi abhabbattepi kammavācāya puggale parāmaṭṭhe kammassa sijjhanato. 
1220269,211,848,36,50,1,110,13,"Upasampadāpekkhassa pana yathāsakaṃ nāmaṃ vinā aññena nāmena anussāvite kammaṃ kuppati, so anupasampannova hoti. "
