1220317,211,857,2,25,1,99,13,"Idāni yamatthaṃ ñāpetukāmo‘‘ suṇātū’’ ti saṅghaṃ savane niyojeti, taṃ ñāpento‘‘ ayaṃ itthannāmo’’ tiādimāha. "
1220318,211,857,26,51,1,176,20,"Tattha ayan ti upasampadāpekkhassa hatthapāse sannihitabhāvadassanaṃ, tena ca hatthapāse ṭhitasseva upasampadā ruhatīti sijjhati hatthapāsato bahi ṭhitassa‘‘ ayan’’ ti na vattabbato. "
1220319,211,857,52,73,1,132,15,"Teneva anusāsakasammutiyaṃ so hatthapāsato bahi ṭhitattā‘‘ ayan’’ ti na vutto, tasmā upasampadāpekkho anupasampanno hatthapāse ṭhapetabbo. "
1220320,211,857,74,88,1,100,12,"Ayaṃ {itthannāmo}ti ayaṃ-saddo ca avassaṃ payujjitabbo, so ca imasmiṃ paṭhamanāmapayoge evāti gahetabbaṃ."
1220321,211,857,89,104,1,96,10,"‘‘ Itthannāmo’’ ti idaṃ aniyamato tassa nāmadassanaṃ, ubhayenapi ayaṃ buddharakkhitotiādināmaṃ dasseti."
1220322,211,857,105,119,1,99,9,"‘‘ Upasampadāpekkho’’ ti bhinnādhikaraṇavisaye bahubbīhisamāso, upasampadaṃ me saṅgho apekkhamānoti attho. "
1220323,211,857,120,133,1,78,9,Tassa ca upajjhāyataṃ samaṅgibhāvena dassetuṃ‘‘ itthannāmassa āyasmato’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1220324,211,857,134,152,1,141,14,Etena‘‘ ayaṃ buddharakkhito āyasmato dhammarakkhitassa saddhivihārikabhūto upasampadāpekkho’’ ti evamādinā nayena nāmayojanāya saha attho dassito. 
1220325,211,857,153,174,1,108,13,Ettha ca‘‘ āyasmato’’ ti padaṃ avatvāpi‘‘ ayaṃ buddharakkhito dhammarakkhitassa upasampadāpekkho’’ ti vattuṃ vaṭṭati. 
1220326,211,857,175,194,1,76,11,Teneva pāḷiyaṃ‘‘ itthannāmena upajjhāyenā’’ ti ettha‘‘ āyasmato’’ ti padaṃ na vuttaṃ. 
1220327,211,857,195,201,1,40,5,"Yañcettha vattabbaṃ, taṃ heṭṭhā vuttameva. "
1220328,211,858,2,30,1,207,23,"Nanu cettha upajjhāyopi upasampadāpekkho viya hatthapāse ṭhito eva icchitabbo, atha kasmā‘‘ ayaṃ itthannāmo imassa itthannāmassa upasampadāpekkho’’ ti evaṃ upajjhāyassa nāmaparāmasanepi idaṃ-saddappayogo na katoti? "
1220329,211,858,31,36,1,52,5,Nāyaṃ virodho upajjhāyassa abhāvepi kammakopābhāvato. 
1220330,211,858,37,61,1,229,19,"Kevalañhi kammanibbattiyā santapadavasena avijjamānassapi upajjhāyassa nāmakittanaṃ anupajjhāyassa upasampadādīsupi karīyati, tasmā upajjhāyassa asannihitāyapi tapparāmasanamatteneva kammasiddhito‘‘ imassā’’ ti niddisituṃ na vaṭṭatīti. "
1220331,211,859,2,15,1,157,12,Parisuddho antarāyikehi {dhammehī}ti abhabbattādikehi upasampadāya avatthukarehi ceva pañcābādhahatthacchinnādīhi āpattikarehi ca antarāyikasabhāvehi parimutto. 
1220332,211,859,16,27,1,90,9,"Evaṃ vutte eva āpattimattakarehi pañcābādhādīhi aparimuttassapi upasampadā ruhati, nāññathā. "
1220333,211,859,28,34,1,76,6,Paripuṇṇassa pattacīvaran ti paripuṇṇamassa upasampadāpekkhassa pattacīvaraṃ. 
