1220958,211,950,70,129,1,358,39,"Yaṃ panettha sāratthadīpaniyaṃ( sārattha. ṭī. mahāvagga3.147)‘‘ tassa antohatthapāsaṃ vijahitvā ṭhito kammaṃ {kopetī}ti iminā paricchedato bahi yattha katthaci ṭhito kammaṃ na kopetī’’ ti vatvā mātikāṭṭhakathāvacanampi paṭikkhipitvā‘‘ neva pāḷiyaṃ na aṭṭhakathāyaṃ upalabbhatī’’ tiādi bahu papañcitaṃ, taṃ na sundaraṃ idha aṭṭhakathāvacanena mātikāṭṭhakathāvacanassa nayato saṃsandanato saṅghaṭanato. "
1220959,211,950,130,172,1,325,34,"Tathā hi dvinnaṃ udakukkhepapaacchedānamantarā vidatthicaturaṅgulamattampi sīmantarikaṃ aṭhapetvā‘‘ añño udakukkhepo sīmantarikāya ṭhapetabbo,‘‘ tato adhikaṃ vaṭṭati eva, ūnakaṃ pana na vaṭṭatī’’ ti evaṃ idheva vuttena iminā aṭṭhakathāvacanena sīmantarikopacāre udakukkhepato ūnake ṭhapite sīmāya sīmāsambhedato kammakopopi vutto eva. "
