1221364,211,1023,20,24,1,40,4,Paraṃ bhikkhusahassaṃ gaṇhantīpi vaṭṭati. 
1221365,211,1023,25,39,1,53,5,Vuttañhi aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( mahāva.138)‘‘ sā heṭṭhimaparicchedenā’’ tiādi. 
1221366,211,1023,40,56,1,152,14,"Ekavīsati {bhikkhū}ti ca nisinne sandhāya vuttaṃ, idañca abbhānakaraṇakāle kammārahabhikkhunā saddhiṃ vīsatigaṇassa saṅghassa nisīdanappahonakatthaṃ vuttaṃ. "
