1221368,211,1023,80,89,1,89,9,Taṃ khaṇḍasīmaṃ bandhantehi bhikkhūhi sīmamāḷakassa samantā nimittūpagā pāsāṇā ṭhapetabbā. 
1221369,211,1023,90,94,1,50,4,Antokhaṇḍasīmāyameva ṭhatvā khaṇḍasīmā bandhitabbā.
1221370,211,1023,95,115,1,136,15,"‘‘ Eso pāsāṇo nimittan’’ ti evaṃ nimittāni kittetvā kammavācāya sīmā bandhitabbā, tassāyeva sīmāya daḷhīkammatthaṃ avippavāsakammavācā kātabbā. "
1221371,211,1023,116,132,1,45,5,Vuttañhi aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( mahāva. aṭṭha.138)‘‘ taṃ bandhantehī’’ tiādi. 
1221372,211,1023,133,139,1,62,6,Evaṃ khaṇḍasīmaṃ sammannitvā bahi sīmantarikapāsāṇā ṭhapetabbā. 
1221373,211,1023,140,149,1,98,7,"Sīmantarikā pacchimakoṭiyā ekaratanappamāṇā vaṭṭati, vidatthippamāṇāpi caturaṅgulappamāṇāpi vaṭṭati. "
1221374,211,1023,150,161,1,77,10,"Sace pana vihāro mahā hoti, dvepi tissopi tatuttaripi khaṇḍasīmāyo bandhitabbā. "
1221375,211,1023,162,171,1,47,5,Vuttañhi aṭṭhakathāyaṃ‘‘ sīmaṃ sammannitvā’’ tiādi. 
1221376,211,1024,2,27,1,298,24,"Evaṃ khaṇḍasīmaṃ sammannitvā mahāsīmāsammutikāle khaṇḍasīmato nikkhamitvā mahāsīmāya ṭhatvā samantā anupariyāyantehi sīmantarikapāsāṇā kittetabbā, tato avasesanimittāni kittetvā hatthapāsaṃ avijahantehi kammavācāya samānasaṃvāsakasīmaṃ sammannitvā tassa daḷhīkammatthaṃ avippavāsakammavācāpi kātabbā. "
