1221390,211,1026,68,74,1,57,6,Evaṃ khaṇḍasīmamahāsīmabandhanena bhikkhūnaṃ ko guṇoti ce? 
1221391,211,1026,75,103,1,209,26,"Evaṃ baddhāsu pana sīmāsu khaṇḍasīmāya ṭhitā bhikkhū mahāsīmāyaṃ kammaṃ karontānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kammaṃ na kopenti, mahāsīmāya vā ṭhitā khaṇḍasīmāya kammaṃ karontānaṃ, sīmantarikāya pana ṭhitā ubhinnampi na kopenti. "
