1221398,211,1029,2,4,1,31,2,25 . Uposathapavāraṇāvinicchayakathā 
1221399,211,1030,2,19,1,107,9,168. Evaṃ sīmāvinicchayaṃ kathetvā idāni uposathapavāraṇāvinicchayaṃ kathetuṃ‘‘ uposathapavāraṇāti ettha’’ tyādimāha. 
1221400,211,1030,20,23,1,25,3,Tattha uposathasaddo tāva–
1221401,211,1031,2,9,1,40,4,"‘ ‘ Uddese pātimokkhassa, paṇṇattiyamuposatho; "
1221402,211,1032,2,11,1,40,6,"Upavāse ca aṭṭhaṅge, uposathadine siyā’’ ti."
1221403,211,1032,12,12,1,0,0,– 
1221404,211,1033,2,10,1,81,8,Vacanato pātimokkhuddese paṇṇattiyaṃ upavāse aṭṭhaṅgasīle uposathadine ca vattati. 
1221405,211,1033,11,112,1,267,31,"Tathā hesa‘‘ āyāmāvuso kappina uposathaṃ gamissāmā’’ tiādīsu( dī. ni. aṭṭha.1.150; ma. ni. aṭṭha.3.85) pātimokkhuddese āgato,‘‘ uposatho nāma nāgarājā’’ tiādīsu( dī. ni.2.246) paṇṇattiyaṃ,‘‘ suddhassa ve sadā pheggu, suddhassa uposatho sadā’’ tiādīsu( ma. ni.1.79) upavāse,‘‘ evaṃ aṭṭhaṅgasamannāgato kho, visākhe, uposatho upavuttho’’ tiādīsu( a. ni.8.43) aṭṭhaṅgasīle."
1221406,211,1033,113,133,1,85,9,"‘‘ Na, bhikkhave, uposathe sabhikkhukāāvāsā abhikkhuko āvāso’’ tiādīsu( pāci.1048) uposathadine vattati."
1221407,211,1033,134,143,1,78,5,‘‘ Pārisuddhiuposatho adhiṭṭhānuposatho’’ tiādīsu pārisuddhiadhiṭṭhānesupi vattati. 
1221408,211,1033,144,152,1,56,8,Te pana pātimokkhuddese antogadhāti katvā visuṃ na vuttā. 
1221409,211,1033,153,159,1,49,6,Idha pana pātimokkhuddese uposathadine ca vattati. 
1221410,211,1033,160,169,1,76,8,"Tattha pātimokkhuddese upavasanaṃ uposatho, sīlena upetā hutvā vasanantyattho. "
1221411,211,1033,170,181,1,89,10,"Uposathadine upavasanti etthāti uposatho, etasmiṃ divase sīlena upetā hutvā vasantītyattho. "
1221412,211,1034,2,20,1,125,13,"Pavāraṇā-saddo pana‘‘ pavāraṇā paṭikkhepe, kathitājjhesanāya cā’’ ti abhidhānappadīpikāyaṃ vacanato paṭikkhepe ajjhesane ca vattati. "
1221413,211,1034,21,80,1,219,26,"Tattha‘‘ yo pana bhikkhu bhuttāvī pavārito anatirittaṃ khādanīyaṃ vā bhojanīyaṃ vā khādeyya vā bhuñjeyya vā, pācittiyan’’ tiādīsu( pāci.238) paṭikkhepe,‘‘ saṅgho pavāreyyā’’ tiādīsu( mahāva.210) ajjhesane,‘‘ ajjapavāraṇā cātuddasī’’ tiādīsu( mahāva. aṭṭha.212) pavāraṇādivase. "
1221414,211,1034,81,87,1,44,6,So pana ajjhesanadivasoyevāti visuṃ na vutto. 
