1221416,211,1034,100,103,1,33,3,Pa-pubba varadhātu curādigaṇikāyaṃ. 
1221417,211,1035,2,33,1,320,28,"Ettha ca kiñcāpi pāḷiyaṃ uposathakkhandhakānantaraṃ vassūpanāyikakkhandhako, tadanantaraṃ pavāraṇakkhandhako saṅgīto, tathāpi uposathapavāraṇakammānaṃ yebhuyyena samānattā yamakamiva bhūtattā missetvā kathento suviññeyyo hoti sallahukagantho cāti mantvā khandhakadvayasaṅgahitaṃ atthaṃ ekeneva paricchedena dasseti ācariyo. "
