1221421,211,1035,56,69,1,144,13,Hemantagimhavassānaṃ tiṇṇaṃ utūnan ti ettha hemantautu nāma aparakattikakāḷapakkhassa pāṭipadato paṭṭhāya phaggunapuṇṇamapariyosānā cattāro māsā. 
