1221788,211,1145,2,23,1,101,16,Assatiyā pana vassaṃ na {upetī}ti‘‘ imasmiṃ vihāre imaṃ temāsaṃ vassaṃ upemī’’ ti vacībhedaṃ katvā na upeti.
1221789,211,1145,24,59,1,186,20,"‘‘ Na, bhikkhave, asenāsanikena vassaṃ upagantabbaṃ, yo upagaccheyya, āpatti dukkaṭassā’’ ti( mahāva.204) vacībhedaṃ katvā vassūpagamanaṃ sandhāya paṭikkhepo, na ālayakaraṇavasena upagamanaṃ sandhāyāti vadanti. "
1221790,211,1145,60,98,1,264,25,"Pāḷiyaṃ pana avisesena vuttattā aṭṭhakathāyañca dutiyapārājikasaṃvaṇṇanāyaṃ( pārā. aṭṭha.1.84)‘‘ vassaṃ upagacchantena hi nālakapaṭipadaṃ paṭipannenapi pañcannaṃ chadanānaṃ aññatarena channeyeva sadvārabandhe senāsane upagantabbaṃ, tasmā vassakāle sace senāsanaṃ labhati, iccetaṃ kusalaṃ. "
1221791,211,1145,99,106,1,49,6,"No ce labhati, hatthakammaṃ pariyesitvāpi kātabbaṃ. "
1221792,211,1145,107,138,1,197,23,"Hatthakammaṃ alabhantena sāmampi kātabbaṃ, na tveva asenāsanikena vassaṃ upagantabban’’ ti( mahāva.204) daḷhaṃ katvā vuttattā asenāsanikassa nāvādiṃ vinā aññattha ālayamattena upagantuṃ na vaṭṭatīti amhākaṃ khanti. "
1221793,211,1145,139,185,1,200,23,"Nāvāsatthavajesuyeva hi‘‘ anujānāmi, bhikkhave, nāvāya vassaṃ upagantun’’ tiādinā( mahāva.203) sati, asati vā senāsane vassūpagamanassa visuṃ anuññātattā‘‘ na, bhikkhave, asenāsanikena vassaṃ upagantabban’’ ti( mahāva.204) ayaṃ paṭikkhepo. "
1221794,211,1145,186,196,1,75,9,Tattha na {labhatī}ti asati senāsane ālayavasenapi nāvādīsu upagamanaṃ vuttaṃ. 
1221795,211,1145,197,205,1,65,7,"Catūsu hi senāsanesu vihārasenāsanaṃ idhādhippetaṃ, na itarattayaṃ. "
1221796,211,1146,2,25,1,150,19,"Ṭaṅkitamañcādibhedā {kuṭī}ti ettha ṭaṅkitamañco nāma dīghe mañcapāde majjhe vijjhitvā aṭaniyo pavesetvā kato mañco, tassa idaṃ upari, idaṃ heṭṭhāti natthi. "
1221797,211,1146,26,51,1,152,19,"Parivattetvā atthatopi tādisova hoti, taṃ susāne devaṭṭhāne ca ṭhapenti, catunnaṃ pāsāṇānaṃ upari pāsāṇaṃ attharitvā kataṃ gehampi‘‘ ṭaṅkitamañco’’ ti vuccati."
1221798,211,1147,2,33,1,132,20,‘ ‘ Idha vassaṃ upemī’’ ti tikkhattuṃ vattabban ti satthassa avihārattā‘‘ imasmiṃ vihāre’’ ti avatvā‘‘ idha vassaṃ upemī’’ ti ettakameva vattabbaṃ. 
1221799,211,1147,34,60,1,162,20,"Satthe pana vassaṃ upagantuṃ na {vaṭṭatī}ti kuṭikādīnaṃ abhāvena‘‘ idha vassaṃ upemī’’ ti vacībhedaṃ katvā upagantuṃ na vaṭṭati, ālayakaraṇamatteneva vaṭṭatīti adhippāyo. "
1221800,211,1147,61,66,1,34,4,{Vippakiratī}ti visuṃ visuṃ gacchati. 
1221801,211,1147,67,89,1,144,18,"Tīsu ṭhānesu natthi vassacchede {āpattī}ti tehi saddhiṃ gacchantasseva natthi āpatti, tehi viyujjitvā gamane pana āpattiyeva, pavāretuñca na labhati. "
