1221814,211,1149,267,279,1,130,12,Ettha ca anupāsakehipi sāsanabhāvaṃ ñātukāmehi pahite tesaṃ pasādavaḍḍhisampattehipi sattāhakaraṇīyena gantuṃ vaṭṭatīti gahetabbaṃ. 
