1221829,211,1151,53,80,1,188,18,"Ācariyaṃ passissāmīti pana gantuṃ {labhatī}ti‘‘ agilānampi ācariyaṃ, upajjhāyaṃ vā passissāmī’’ ti sattāhakaraṇīyena gantuṃ labhati, nissayācariyaṃ dhammācariyañca, pageva upasampadācariyaupajjhāye. "
