1221831,211,1151,123,130,1,72,7,Vassacchedo pana hotiyevāti daṭṭhabbaṃ sattāhassa bahiddhā vītināmitattā. 
1221832,211,1152,2,16,1,123,13,Sace dūraṃ gato sattāhavārena aruṇo {uṭṭhāpetabbo}ti iminā vassacchedakāraṇe sati sattāhakaraṇīyena gantumpi vaṭṭatīti dīpeti. 
1221833,211,1152,17,35,1,167,18,Ettha cha divasāni bahiddhā vītināmetvā sattame divase purāruṇā eva antoupacārasīmāyaṃ pavisitvā aruṇaṃ uṭṭhāpetvā punadivase sattāhaṃ adhiṭṭhāya gantabbanti adhippāyo. 
1221834,211,1152,36,65,1,150,20,"Keci pana‘‘ sattame divase āgantvā aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā tadaheva divasabhāgepi gantuṃ vaṭṭatī’’ ti vadanti, taṃ na gahetabbaṃ‘‘ aruṇo uṭṭhāpetabbo’’ ti vuttattā. "
1221835,211,1152,66,87,1,97,12,Sattame divase tattha aruṇuṭṭhāpanameva hi sandhāya pāḷiyaṃ( mahāva.199)‘‘ sattāhaṃ sannivatto kātabbo’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
1221836,211,1152,88,105,1,147,17,Aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā gacchanto ca anto appavisitvā bahiddhāva sattāhaṃ vītināmento ca samucchinnavasso eva bhavissati aruṇassa bahi eva uṭṭhāpitattā. 
1221837,211,1152,106,117,1,55,7,Itarathā‘‘ aruṇo uṭṭhāpetabbo’’ ti vacanaṃ niratthakaṃ siyā.
1221838,211,1152,118,136,1,122,13,‘‘ Sattāhavārena antovihāre pavisitvā aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā gantabban’’ ti vattabbato aññesu ca ṭhānesu aruṇuṭṭhāpanameva vuccati. 
1221839,211,1152,137,159,1,98,11,Vakkhati hi cīvarakkhandhake( mahāva. aṭṭha.364)‘‘ ekasmiṃ vihāre vasanto itarasmiṃ sattāhavārena aruṇameva uṭṭhāpetī’’ ti. 
1221840,211,1153,2,31,1,181,23,"Athāpi yaṃ te vadeyyuṃ‘‘ sattame divase yadā kadāci paviṭṭhena taṃdivasanissito atītāruṇo uṭṭhāpito nāma hotīti imamatthaṃ sandhāya aṭṭhakathāyaṃ vuttan’’ ti, taṃ saddagatiyāpi na sameti. "
1221841,211,1153,32,42,1,76,10,Na hi uṭṭhite aruṇe pacchā paviṭṭho tassa payojako uṭṭhāpako bhavitumarahati. 
1221842,211,1153,43,76,1,150,17,"Yadi bhaveyya,‘‘ vassaṃ upagantvā pana aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā tadaheva sattāhakaraṇīyena pakkamantassā’’ pīti( mahāva. aṭṭha.207) ettha‘‘ aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā’’ ti vacanaṃ virujjheyya. "
1221843,211,1153,77,103,1,242,25,"Tenapi taṃdivasanissitassa aruṇassa uṭṭhāpitattā āraññakassapi bhikkhuno sāyanhasamaye aṅgayuttaṃ araññaṃ gantvā tadā eva nivattantassa aruṇo uṭṭhāpito dhutaṅgañca visodhitaṃ siyā, na cetaṃ yuttaṃ aruṇuggamanakāle eva aruṇuṭṭhāpanassa vuttattā. "
1221844,211,1153,104,114,1,72,8,Vuttañhi‘‘ kālasseva pana nikkhamitvā aṅgayutte ṭhāne aruṇaṃ uṭṭhāpetabbaṃ. 
1221845,211,1153,115,139,1,110,13,"Sace aruṇuṭṭhānavelāyaṃ tesaṃ ābādho vaḍḍhati, tesaṃ eva kiccaṃ kātabbaṃ, na dhutaṅgavisuddhikena bhavitabban’’ ti( visuddhi.1.31). "
1221846,211,1153,140,148,1,83,8,Tathā pārivāsikādīnampi aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā vattaṃ nikkhipantānaṃ ratticchedo vutto.
1221847,211,1153,149,166,1,40,6,‘‘ Uggate aruṇe nikkhipitabban’’ ti( cūḷava. aṭṭha.97) hi vuttaṃ. 
1221848,211,1153,167,184,1,106,8,Sahaseyyasikkhāpadepi anupasampannehi saha nivutthabhāvaparimocanatthaṃ‘‘ purāruṇā nikkhamitvā’’ tiādi( pāci.54) vuttaṃ. 
1221849,211,1153,185,203,1,186,16,"Evaṃ cīvaravippavāsādīsu ca sabbattha rattipariyosāne āgāmiaruṇavaseneva aruṇuṭṭhānaṃ dassitaṃ, na atītāruṇavasena, tasmā vuttanayenevettha aruṇuṭṭhāpanaṃ veditabbaṃ aññathā vassacchedattā. "
1221850,211,1154,2,40,1,271,31,"Yaṃ pana vassaṃ upagatassa tadaheva aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā sakaraṇīyassa pakkamanavacanaṃ, taṃ vassaṃ upagatakālato paṭṭhāya yadā kadāci nimitte sati gamanassa anuññātattā yuttaṃ, na pana sattāhavārena gatassa aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā tadahevagamanaṃ ‘‘ aruṇo uṭṭhāpetabbo’’ ti vuttattā. "
1221851,211,1154,41,77,1,194,24,"Yathā vā‘‘ sattāhānāgatāya pavāraṇāya sakaraṇīyo pakkamati, āgaccheyya vā so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu taṃ āvāsaṃ na vā āgaccheyyā’’ tiādinā( mahāva.207) pacchimasattāhe anāgamane anuññātepi aññasattāhesu taṃ na vaṭṭati. "
1221852,211,1154,78,97,1,156,18,Evaṃ paṭhamasattāhe aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā gamane anuññātepi tato paresu sattāhesu āgatassa aruṇaṃ anuṭṭhāpetvā gamanaṃ na vaṭṭati evāti niṭṭhamettha gantabbaṃ. 
1221853,211,1155,2,12,1,126,9,Sace pavāritakāle vassāvāsikaṃ {dentī}tiādinā vassāvāsikacīvarampi kathinacīvaraṃ viya vassaṃvutthavihārapaṭibaddhanti viññāyati.
