1222068,211,1194,27,58,1,176,19,"Tattha ko {ācariyo}ti‘‘ anujānāmi, bhikkhave, dasavassaṃ nissāya vatthuṃ dasavassena nissayaṃ dātun’’ tiādivacanato( mahāva.77) byattibalasampanno dasavasso vā atirekadasavasso vā bhikkhu ācariyo. "
