1222078,211,1195,20,62,1,266,33,"Ettha sacāyaṃ bhikkhu vuḍḍhataraṃ ācariyaṃ na labhati, upasampadāya saṭṭhivasso vā sattativasso vā hoti, navakatarassapi byattassa santike ukkuṭikaṃ nisīditvā añjaliṃ paggahetvā‘‘ ācariyo me, āvuso, hohi, āyasmato nissāya vacchāmī’’ ti evaṃ tikkhattuṃ vatvā nissayo gahetabbo. "
