1223075,211,1399,51,82,1,148,19,Tato‘‘ evaṃ duvaṅgasampanno puggalo antosīmaṭṭho vā bahisīmaṭṭho vā’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ antosīmaṭṭho’’ ti vutte‘‘ sādhu suṭṭhu tassa dātabbo’’ ti sampaṭicchitabbaṃ.
1223076,211,1399,83,98,1,52,7,‘‘ Bahisīmaṭṭho’’ ti vutte‘‘ na dātabbo’’ ti paṭikkhipitabbaṃ. 
1223077,211,1399,99,101,1,10,2,Kasmāti ce?
