1223079,211,1400,2,32,1,156,18,Atha ‘‘ duvaṅgasamannāgate antosīmaṭṭhe asati ekaṅgasamannāgato antosīmaṭṭho atthī’’ ti pucchitvā‘‘ atthī’’ ti vutte‘‘ sādhu suṭṭhu etassa dātabbo’’ ti sampaṭicchitabbaṃ. 
1223080,211,1400,33,36,1,21,3,Kathaṃ viññāyatīti ce?
