1223158,211,1421,67,86,1,208,18,Bahisīmaṭṭhakesu bhikkhūsu vicinitvā yathāvuttaaṅgayuttapuggale labbhamāne taṃ puggalaṃ antosīmaṃ pavesetvā antosīmaṭṭhakassa saṅghassa anumatiyā dhuvavāsatthāya vihāraṃ sammannitvā anuṭṭhāpanīyaṃ katvā detha. 
