1223477,211,1488,29,52,1,126,12,Tena ca tasmiṃyeva sīmamaṇḍale adhiṭṭhahitvā attharitvā saṅgho anumodāpetabbo’’ ti vuttena vajirabuddhiṭīkāvacanena( vajira. ṭī. mahāvagga308) virujjhatīti? 
