1223668,211,1518,75,97,1,157,17,"Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ– anujānāmi, bhikkhave, paṭhamaṃ uccinitvā tulayitvā vaṇṇāvaṇṇaṃ katvā bhikkhū gaṇetvā vaggaṃ bandhitvā cīvarapaṭivīsaṃ ṭhapetun’’ ti. "
1223669,211,1518,98,140,1,177,23,"Aṭṭhakathāyañca( mahāva. aṭṭha.343)‘‘ {uccinitvā}ti‘ idaṃ thūlaṃ, idaṃ saṇhaṃ, idaṃ ghanaṃ, idaṃ tanukaṃ, idaṃ paribhuttaṃ, idaṃ aparibhuttaṃ, idaṃ dīghato ettakaṃ, puthulato ettakan’ ti evaṃ vatthāni vicinitvā. "
