1223770,211,1545,2,8,1,61,6,Kasmā pana antarubbhāravasena kammavācāya kathinaṃ ubbhatanti? 
1223771,211,1545,9,17,1,83,8,Mahādānaṃ dātukāmehi upāsakehi āgatassa saṅghassa akālacīvaraṃ dātukāmehi yācitattā. 
1223772,211,1545,18,47,1,181,21,"Vuttañhi bhikkhunīvibhaṅgapāḷiyaṃ( pāci.925)‘‘ tena kho pana samayena aññatarena upāsakena saṅghaṃ uddissa vihāro kārāpito hoti, so tassa vihārassa mahe ubhatosaṅghassa akālacīvaraṃ dātukāmo hoti. "
1223773,211,1545,48,56,1,61,8,Tena kho pana samayena ubhatosaṅghassa kathinaṃ atthataṃ hoti. 
1223774,211,1545,57,68,1,68,9,Atha kho so upāsako saṅghaṃ upasaṅkamitvā kathinuddhāraṃ yācī’’ tiādi. 
