1224435,211,1665,12,40,1,168,17,"Tattha {kāraṇacchāyā}ti suttādīsu‘‘ kappiyan’’ ti gāhassa,‘‘ akappiyan’’ ti gāhassa ca nimittabhūtena kicchena paṭipādanīyaṃ avibhūtakāraṇaṃ kāraṇacchāyā, kāraṇapatirūpakanti attho. "
