1224973,211,1754,55,70,1,115,12,"Tenāha‘‘ gumbena vā vatiyā vā paṭicchannaṭṭhāne nisīditabbaṃ, antoaruṇeyeva vuttanayena vattaṃ samādiyitvā ārocetabbaṃ. "
1224974,211,1754,71,91,1,118,17,"Sace añño koci bhikkhu kenacideva karaṇīyena taṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchati, sace esa taṃ passati, saddaṃ vāssa suṇāti, ārocetabbaṃ. "
1224975,211,1754,92,97,1,44,5,Anārocentassa ratticchedo ceva vattabhedo ca. 
