1224984,211,1756,2,30,1,312,26,Pañcamapāṭhassa pana ayamadhippāyo– atthibhāvaṃ {sallakkhetvā}ti ettha etasmiṃ aṭṭhakathāvacane nikkhittavattānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ attano nisinnaṭṭhānato dvādasahatthe upacāre aññesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ atthibhāvaṃ sallakkhetvā anikkhittavattānaṃ upacārasīmāya aññesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ āgatabhāvaṃ sallakkhetvā sahavāsādikaṃ veditabbaṃ. 
