1224996,211,1757,78,91,1,140,12,"Bahiupacārasīmāya hi parivasantassa bhikkhussa sakalasarīraṃ pakatattabhikkhūnaṃ antodvādasahatthe upacāre ṭhapetabbaṃ hoti, na ekadesamattaṃ. "
1224997,211,1758,2,29,1,194,22,"Tesaṃ pana ayamadhippāyo siyā– dvādasahatthappadesato sakalasarīrassa antokaraṇe sati sahavāso bhaveyya, bahikaraṇe sati vippavāso, tena upaḍḍhaṃ anto upaḍḍhaṃ bahi hotūti, taṃ micchāñāṇavasena hoti. "
