1225123,211,1779,2,78,1,414,47,"Atha pana vinayadharena puṭṭho‘‘ ahaṃ, bhante, sambahulā saṅghādisesā āpattiyo āpajjiṃ ekaṃ sukkavissaṭṭhiṃ, ekaṃ kāyasaṃsaggaṃ, ekaṃ duṭṭhullavācaṃ, ekaṃ attakāmaṃ, ekaṃ sañcarittaṃ, ekaṃ kuṭikāraṃ, ekaṃ vihārakāraṃ, ekaṃ duṭṭhadosaṃ, ekaṃ aññabhāgiyaṃ, ekaṃ saṅghabhedaṃ, ekaṃ bhedānuvattakaṃ, ekaṃ dubbacaṃ, ekaṃ kuladūsakan’’ ti vutte‘‘ ayaṃ bhikkhu missakasamodhānaparivāsāraho’’ ti ñatvā aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( cūḷava. aṭṭha.102) āgatanayena parivāso dātabbo. "
1225124,211,1779,79,87,1,69,6,"Etthāha– agghasamodhānamissakasamodhānānaṃ ko viseso, kiṃ nānākaraṇanti? "
1225125,211,1779,88,113,1,258,21,"Vuccate– agghasamodhānaparivāso acirappaṭicchannā āpattiyo cirappaṭicchannāyaṃ āpattiyaṃ samodhānetvā tassā cirappaṭicchannāya āpattiyā agghavasena dīyati, missakasamodhānaparivāso nānāvatthukā āpattiyo samodhānetvā tāsaṃ missakavasena dīyati, ayametesaṃ viseso. "
1225126,211,1779,114,125,1,105,10,"Atha vā agghasamodhāno sabhāgavatthūnaṃ āpattīnaṃ samodhānavasena hoti, itaro visabhāgavatthūnanti ācariyā. "
1225127,211,1779,126,157,1,205,18,"Tenevāha ācariyavajirabuddhitthero( vajira. ṭī. cūḷavagga102)‘‘ agghasamodhāno nāma sabhāgavatthukāyo sambahulā āpattiyo āpannassa bahurattiṃ paṭicchāditāpattiyaṃ nikkhipitvā dātabbo, itaro nānāvatthukānaṃ vasenāti ayametesaṃ viseso’’ ti. "
1225128,211,1780,2,28,1,175,21,"Atha siyā‘‘ evaṃ cirappaṭicchannāyo ca acirappaṭicchannāyo ca nānāvatthukāyo āpattiyo āpajjantassa ko parivāso dātabbo agghasamodhāno vā missakasamodhāno vā, atha tadubhayā vā’’ ti. "
1225129,211,1780,29,50,1,196,18,"Kiñcettha– yadi agghasamodhānaṃ dadeyya, cirappaṭicchannāhi ca acirappaṭicchannāhi ca sabhāgavatthukāhi āpattīhi vuṭṭhito bhaveyya, cirappaṭicchannāhi ca acirappaṭicchannāhi ca no visabhāgavatthukāhi. "
1225130,211,1780,51,87,1,257,27,"Yadi ca missakasamodhānaṃ dadeyya, samānakālappaṭicchannāhi visabhāgavatthūhi āpattīhi vuṭṭhito bhaveyya, no asamānakaālappaṭicchannāhi sabhāgavatthukāhi ca, atha tadubhayampi dadeyya,‘‘ ekasmiṃ kamme dve parivāsā dātabbā’’ ti neva pāḷiyaṃ, na aṭṭhakathāyaṃ vuttanti? "
1225131,211,1780,88,104,1,129,15,Vuccate– idañhi sabbampi parivāsādikaṃ vinayakammaṃ vatthuvasena vā gottavasena vā nāmavasena vā āpattivasena vā kātuṃ vaṭṭatiyeva. 
