1226596,211,2084,36,64,1,174,22,"So hi rājaputto aputtako, sutañcānena ahosi‘ buddhānaṃ kira adhikāraṃ katvā manasā icchitaṃ labhantī’ ti, so‘ sacāhaṃ puttaṃ labhissāmi, sammāsambuddho imaṃ celapaṭikaṃ akkamissati. "
