1227242,211,2184,96,100,1,37,4,Kittakaṃ pana cīvaraṃ vikappetabbanti?
1227243,211,2184,101,131,1,219,19,"‘‘ Anujānāmi, bhikkhave, āyāmena aṭṭhaṅgulaṃ sugataṅgulena caturaṅgulavitthataṃ pacchimaṃ cīvaraṃ vikappetun’’ ti( mahāva.358) vacanato sabbantimena paricchedena sugataṅgulena aṭṭhaṅgulāyāmaṃ caturaṅgulavitthāraṃ cīvaraṃ vikappetuṃ vaṭṭati. "
1227244,211,2184,132,169,1,403,33,"Tattha sugataṅgulaṃ nāma majjhimapurisaṅgulasaṅkhātena vaḍḍhakīaṅgulena tivaṅgulaṃ hoti, manussānaṃ pakatiaṅgulena aḍḍhapañcakaṅgulaṃ, tasmā dīghato vaḍḍhakīhatthena ekahatthaṃ pakatihatthena diyaḍḍhahatthaṃ vitthārato vaḍḍhakīhatthena vidatthippamāṇaṃ pakatihatthena chaḷaṅgulādhikavidatthippamāṇaṃ pacchimaṃ cīvaraṃ vikappetuṃ vaṭṭati, tato ūnappamāṇaṃ na vaṭṭati, adhikappamāṇaṃ pana vaṭṭatīti daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
1227245,211,2185,2,2,1,14,1,Aṭṭhavarakathā 
1227246,211,2186,2,27,1,231,19,"Aṭṭhavarakathāyaṃ ‘‘ anujānāmi, bhikkhave, vassikasāṭikaṃ āgantukabhattaṃ gamikabhattaṃ gilānabhattaṃ gilānupaṭṭhākabhattaṃ gilānabhesajjaṃ dhuvayāguṃ bhikkhunisaṅghassa udakasāṭikan’’ ti vacanato imāni aṭṭha dānāni sampaṭicchituṃ vaṭṭati. "
1227247,211,2186,28,43,1,127,14,"Tattha nikkhittacīvarā hutvā kāyaṃ ovassantānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ naggiyaṃ asuci jegucchaṃ paṭikūlaṃ hoti, tasmā vassikasāṭikā anuññātā. "
1227248,211,2186,44,87,1,287,34,"Āgantuko bhikkhu na vīthikusalo hoti, na gocarakusalo, kilanto piṇḍāya carati, tasmā āgantukabhattaṃ anuññātaṃ, gamiko bhikkhu attano bhattaṃ pariyesamāno satthā vā vihāyissati , yattha vā vāsaṃ gantukāmo bhavissati, tattha vikālena upagacchissati, kilanto addhānaṃ gamissati, tasmā gamikabhattaṃ. "
1227249,211,2186,88,103,1,123,13,"Gilānassa bhikkhuno sappāyāni bhojanāni alabhantassa ābādho vā abhivaḍḍhissati, kālakiriyā vā bhavissati, tasmā gilānabhattaṃ. "
1227250,211,2186,104,116,1,115,11,"Gilānupaṭṭhāko bhikkhu attano bhattaṃ pariyesamāno gilānassa ussūre bhattaṃ nīharissati, tasmā gilānupaṭṭhākabhattaṃ. "
1227251,211,2186,117,133,1,126,13,"Gilānassa bhikkhuno sappāyāni bhesajjāni alabhantassa ābādho vā abhivaḍḍhissati, kālakiriyā vā bhavissati, tasmā gilānabhesajjaṃ. "
1227252,211,2186,134,144,1,85,9,"Yasmā bhagavatā andhakavinde dasānisaṃse sampassamānena yāgu anuññātā, tasmā dhuvayāgu. "
1227253,211,2186,145,157,1,103,11,"Yasmā mātugāmassa naggiyaṃ asuci jegucchaṃ paṭikūlaṃ hoti, tasmā bhikkhunisaṅghassa udakasāṭikā anuññātā. "
