1227265,211,2189,2,2,1,17,1,Adhammakammakathā 
1227266,211,2190,2,27,1,132,15,"58. Adhammakammakathāyaṃ na, bhikkhave… pe… {dukkaṭassā}ti idaṃ‘‘ tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū saṅghamajjhe adhammakammaṃ karonti. "
1227267,211,2190,28,57,1,149,17,"Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ– na, bhikkhave, adhammakammaṃ kātabbaṃ, yo kareyya, āpatti dukkaṭassā’’ ti( mahāva.154) imaṃ uposathakkhandhake āgatapāṭhaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ. "
1227268,211,2190,58,83,1,138,16,"Anujānāmi… pe… paṭikkositun ti tatheva āgataṃ‘‘ bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ– anujānāmi, bhikkhave, adhammakamme kayiramāne paṭikkositun’’ ti imaṃ. "
1227269,211,2190,84,93,1,87,8,Tattha {karontiyevā}ti paññattampi sikkhāpadaṃ madditvā adhammakammaṃ karontiyevāti attho.
1227270,211,2190,94,132,1,203,25,"‘‘ Anujānāmi… pe… paṭikkositun’’ ti evaṃ adhammakamme kayiramāne sati‘‘ pesalehi bhikkhūhi taṃ adhammakammaṃ akataṃ, kammaṃ dukkaṭaṃ kammaṃ puna kātabban’’ ti evaṃ paṭikkositabbaṃ, na tuṇhībhāvena khamitabbanti attho. "
1227271,211,2190,133,142,1,57,8,Iti {vacanato}ti idaṃ pana pubbapāṭhaṃ gahetvā iti vacanato. 
1227272,211,2190,143,158,1,136,15,Adhammakammaṃ na kātabban ti aparapāṭhaṃ gahetvā iti vacanato kayiramānañca adhammakammaṃ bhikkhūhi nivāretabbanti dvidhā yojanā kātabbā. 
1227273,211,2191,2,30,1,197,22,"Nivārentehi {cā}tiādi pana‘‘ tena kho pana samayena pesalā bhikkhū chabbaggiyehi bhikkhūhi adhammakamme kayiramāne paṭikkosanti, chabbaggiyā bhikkhū labhanti āghātaṃ, labhanti appaccayaṃ, vadhena tajjenti. "
1227274,211,2191,31,67,1,191,21,"Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ– anujānāmi, bhikkhave, diṭṭhimpi āvikātun’’ ti( mahāva.154) pāṭhañca‘‘ tesaṃyeva santike diṭṭhiṃ āvikaronti, chabbaggiyā bhikkhū labhanti āghātaṃ, labhanti appaccayaṃ, vadhena tajjenti. "
1227275,211,2191,68,97,1,169,22,"Bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ– anujānāmi, bhikkhave, catūhi pañcahi paṭikkosituṃ, dvīhi tīhi diṭṭhiṃ āvikātuṃ, ekena adhiṭṭhātuṃ na metaṃ khamatī’’ ti ime pāṭhe sandhāya vuttaṃ. "
