1227446,211,2225,74,86,1,71,8,"Tattha‘‘ {nacchādentī}ti na jīranti, na vātarogaṃ paṭippassambhetuṃ sakkonti. "
1227447,211,2225,87,90,1,23,2,{Senesitānī}ti siniddhāni. 
