1228520,212,106,23,48,1,154,20,"Tattha yo aṭṭhakathāyaṃ‘‘ amanusso nāma yo sabbaso vā manussānaṃ abhāvena yakkhapariggahabhūto’’ ti vutto, so gāmo na gāmaparihāraṃ katthaci sikkhāpade labhati. "
1228521,212,106,49,91,1,132,16,"Yañhi sandhāya aṭṭhakathāyaṃ‘‘ taṃ panetaṃ buddhakāle, cakkavattikāle ca nagaraṃ hoti, sesakāle suññaṃ hoti yakkhapariggahitan’’ ti( pārā. aṭṭha.1.84; dī. ni. aṭṭha.1.150) vuttaṃ. "
