1229181,212,264,210,226,1,107,11,"Taṃ pana atippasaṅgaṃ nivāretuṃ‘‘ niṭṭhitacīvarasmin’’ tiādi vuttaṃ, na kathinadivasāni adivasānīti dīpanatthaṃ. "
1229182,212,264,227,231,1,37,4,Ayamattho tattha tattha āvibhavissati. 
1229183,212,264,232,249,1,150,16,"Atha vā vassikasāṭikā anatirittappamāṇā nāmaṃ gahetvā vuttanayeneva cattāro vassike māse adhiṭṭhātabbā, tato paraṃ paccuddharitvā vikappetabbāti vuttaṃ. "
