1229188,212,267,2,20,1,125,14,‘ ‘ Atthatakathinassa pañca māse baddhasīmāyaṃ yattha katthaci cīvaraṃ nikkhipitvā pakkamantassa anāpattī’’ ti aṭṭhakathāyaṃ vuttaṃ.
1229189,212,267,21,34,1,104,9,‘‘ Abaddhasīmāyapi vaṭṭatī’’ ti idaṃ abaddhasīmāyaṃ kathinatthārañca āraññakasikkhāpadañca sādhetīti likhitaṃ. 
1229190,212,267,35,36,1,5,1,Idāni–
