1229195,212,271,26,45,1,132,15,"Sace adhiṭṭhāti, na ruhatī’’ ti vatvā upasampadāpekkhānampi diguṇaṃyeva saṅghāṭiṃ datvā upasampādenti, te iminā suttalesena saññāpetabbā. "
1229196,212,271,46,63,1,101,11,"Bhagavatā hi‘‘ chinnakaṃ saṅghāṭiṃ, chinnakaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ, chinnakaṃ antaravāsakan’’ ti paṭhamaṃ anuññātaṃ. "
1229197,212,271,64,74,1,73,8,Tato‘‘ aññatarassa bhikkhuno ticīvare kariyamāne sabbaṃ chinnakaṃ nappahoti. 
1229198,212,271,75,114,1,202,24,"Dve chinnakāni ekaṃ achinnakaṃ nappahoti, dve achinnakāni ekaṃ chinnakaṃ nappahotī’’ ti imasmiṃ vatthusmiṃ‘‘ anujānāmi, bhikkhave, anvādhikampi āropetun’’ ti( mahāva.360) anuññātaṃ, tasmā ekaccikāpi saṅghāṭi vaṭṭatīti siddhaṃ. "
