1229404,212,337,53,75,1,154,16,Imasmiṃ pana atthavikappe‘‘ bhikkhuno paneva eḷakalomāni uppajjeyyuṃ… pe… asantepi hārake addhānamaggappaṭipannassa nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyan’’ ti yojanā veditabbā. 
1229405,212,337,76,99,1,176,17,"Yasmā vā eḷakalomānaṃ uppattiṭṭhānato paṭṭhāya tiyojanaparamatā adhippetā, maggaṃ appaṭipannassa ca tiyojanaparamatā natthi, tasmā‘‘ addhānamaggappaṭipannassa uppajjeyyun’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1229406,212,337,100,107,1,56,7,Tena acchinnaṃ paṭilabhitvā harato ca anāpattīti siddhaṃ. 
1229407,212,337,108,113,1,33,5,Paṭilābho hi tesaṃ uppatti nāmāti.
1229408,212,338,2,16,1,108,11,‘ ‘ Ākaṅkhamānena bhikkhunā paṭiggahetabbānī’’ ti iminā attanā paṭiggahitānaṃyeva tiyojanātikkame āpattīti dasseti. 
1229409,212,338,17,24,1,78,7,Tena anākaṅkhamānena parasantakāni paṭiggahitāni harantassa anāpattīti siddhaṃ. 
1229410,212,339,2,34,1,133,18,"Aṅgesu ‘‘ attano santakatā’’ ti natthi, ayamattho‘‘ bhikkhuno uppajjeyyun’’ ti iminā,‘‘ acchinnaṃ paṭilabhitvā’’ ti iminā ca dīpito hotīti veditabbo. "
1229411,212,339,35,51,1,85,11,"Porāṇagaṇṭhipade ca‘‘ aññaṃ bhikkhuṃ harāpento gacchati ce, dvinnampi anāpattī’’ ti vuttaṃ. "
1229412,212,339,52,65,1,103,12,"Tasmā dve bhikkhū tiyojanaparamaṃ patvā aññamaññassa bhaṇḍaṃ parivattetvā ce haranti, anāpattīti siddhaṃ. "
1229413,212,340,2,12,1,92,8,"Tiyojanaparamaṃ sahatthā {haritabbānī}ti tiyojanaparamameva attanā haritabbāni, taṃ kimatthanti? "
1229414,212,340,13,15,1,18,2,Sīmāya etaparamato. 
