1229432,212,352,2,3,1,19,2,Tatridaṃ pakiṇṇakaṃ 
1229433,212,353,2,16,1,161,14,Aṭṭhamasikkhāpadaṃ parena attano atthāya diyyamānassa vā pārivattakabhāvena diyyamānassa vā paṃsukūlassa vā rūpiyassa uggaṇhanauggaṇhāpanasādiyanāni paṭikkhipati. 
1229434,212,354,2,9,1,60,7,Navamaṃ parassa vā attano vā rūpiyaparivattanaṃ paṭikkhipati. 
1229435,212,355,2,6,1,27,2,Dasamaṃ arūpiyaparivattanaṃ.
1229436,212,355,7,45,1,87,12,‘‘ Arūpiye arūpiyasaññī pañcannaṃ saha anāpattī’’ ti( pārā.591; vi. vi. ṭī.1.591; vajira. ṭī. pārājika587) ca vacanaṃ itarehi saha āpattīti dīpeti. 
1229437,212,355,46,48,1,24,2,Arūpiyañca dukkaṭavatthu. 
1229438,212,355,49,56,1,58,7,Tasmā tassa parivattane sati nissaggiyanti ekantena vuttaṃ. 
1229439,212,355,57,66,1,89,9,Pañcannaṃ saha dukkaṭavatthūnaṃ parivattane anāpattippasaṅgato anāpatti evāti porāṇāti ce? 
1229440,212,355,67,72,1,39,4,"Na, kappiyavatthūnaṃyeva tattha āgatattā. "
1229441,212,355,73,80,1,56,6,"Yadi kappiyavatthu nissaggiyaṃ, pageva dukkaṭavatthūti ce? "
1229442,212,355,81,85,1,60,3,"Na, āpattigarukalahukabhāvena vatthugarukalahukaniyamābhāvato. "
1229443,212,356,2,12,1,124,10,Nissaggiyavatthuto hi muttāmaṇiveḷuriyādi mahagghappahonakampi dukkaṭavatthūti katvā nissaggiyavatthuto muttādi lahukaṃ hoti. 
1229444,212,356,13,38,1,135,15,"Lahukepi vatthusmiṃ yatheva dukkaṭavatthuno paṭiggahaṇe dukkaṭaṃ, tatheva tassa vā tena vā cetāpanepi dukkaṭaṃ yuttanti( pārā. aṭṭha.2.589) aṭṭhakathācariyā. "
1229445,212,357,2,27,1,167,19,"Atha vā yaṃ vuttaṃ‘‘ kappiyavatthūnaṃyeva tattha āgatattā’’ ti, tattha kiñcāpi dukkaṭavatthūnipi adhippetāni, na pana pāḷiyaṃ vuttāni anāpattivārappasaṅgabhayāti vuttaṃ hoti. "
1229446,212,357,28,57,1,178,22,"Muttādīsupi vuttesu anāpattiyaṃ kappiyakārakassa ācikkhati,‘‘ idaṃ muttādi amhākaṃ atthi, amhākañca iminā ca iminā ca veḷuriyādinā attho’’ ti bhaṇati, dasamena āpajjatīti adhippāyo siyā. "
1229447,212,357,58,70,1,93,11,"Yasmā ca idaṃ kappiyakārakassa ācikkhanādisaṃvohāro ca, tasmā taṃ navamena vuttanti veditabbaṃ. "
1229448,212,357,71,89,1,171,16,"Kiñcāpi kayavikkayeva hoti kappiyavatthūhi anuññātaṃ, imināva nayena kiñcāpi dukkaṭavatthupi dasame adhippetaṃ āpajjati, aṭṭhakathāvirodhato pana nādhippetamicceva gahetabbo. "
1229449,212,358,2,13,1,85,10,"Kā panettha kāraṇacchāyāti, pañcannaṃ saha tattha anāpattippasaṅgato anāpatti evāti ce? "
1229450,212,358,14,18,1,20,3,"Na, tattha anāgatattā. "
1229451,212,358,19,22,1,25,3,Anāgatakāraṇā vuttanti ce? 
1229452,212,358,23,38,1,145,13,"Na, pañcannaṃ saha āpattivatthukassa anāpattivāralābhe visesakāraṇābhāvā, akappiyattā pañcannaṃ sahāpi āpattiyā bhavitabbanti siddho aṭṭhakathāvādo. "
1229453,212,359,2,22,1,149,17,"Aparo nayo– yadi dukkaṭavatthunā kayavikkaye nissaggiyaṃ, kappiyavatthumhi vuttapariyāyo tattha labbheyya, na pana labbhatīti navame eva tāni vattabbāni. "
1229454,212,359,23,61,1,292,29,"Tasmā saṃvohāro nāma kayavikkayopi aññathā parivattanaṃ pariyādiyitvā pavatto, kayavikkayañca mocetvā ‘‘ iminā imaṃ dehī’ ti cetāpeti, vaṭṭatī’’ ti avatvā dasamassa anāpattivāre vuttanayeneva tesaṃ parivattane nissaggiyānumativirodhato aṭṭhakathāyaṃ vuttanayeneva dukkaṭavatthunā cetāpane dukkaṭameva. "
