1229462,212,360,5,15,1,67,7,"‘‘ attano santakaṃ rūpiyaṃ parahatthagataṃ karoti ajjhācarati, dukkaṭaṃ. "
1229463,212,360,16,24,1,63,7,"Parassa rūpiyaṃ attano hatthagataṃ karoti, aṭṭhamena nissaggiyaṃ. "
